Veer Pahariya (@veerpahariya) didn’t grow up around film sets or casting calls — but the spotlight found him anyway. Since his debut in Sky Force, the internet hasn’t stopped watching. With that smouldery gaze, and a surprisingly sharp on-screen presence, Veer isn’t just arriving — he’s declaring a soft launch era: poised, intentional, and unmistakably Bollywood leading man material.

Veer is wearing the Tissot PRC 100 Solar (@tissot_official, @tatacliqluxury).
